Counsel, 
In accordance with Judge Nathan's Order dated April 29, 2021 (Dkt. No. 257), the Government is sharing its letter so you 
can indicate if you believe any private medical information needs to be redacted before public filing. We do not believe 
any redactions are necessary. Please let us know if you think any redactions are needed. 
Thanks, 
Lara 
Assistant United States Attorney
